Feature: App allows for users to register and create an account.

  Scenario: Register new user
    Given I register new user
    When I create a new user
      | Name     | Login | Password | Password confirmation |
      | Alex New | alex  | 1234     | 1234                  |
    Then I should be logged in as "Alex New"

  Scenario: Login with existing user
    Given Existing accounts
      | name          | login | password | password_confirmation |
      | Alex Existing | alex  | 1234     | 1234                  |
    When I login with "alex" - "1234"
    Then I should be logged in as "Alex Existing"
